The paper deals with the optimization of deep neural networks, which is a core topic in machine learning (cs.LG). The experiments are conducted on two popular models, BERT and ResNet-50, which are commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and computer vision (cs.CV) respectively. The paper also discusses the use of TPUs, which are specialized hardware for machine learning (cs.AI, cs.DC). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, and cs.DC.
